Dangote Cement has announced a N20 dividend per share for the end of the 2022 financial year. This was revealed in the 2022 audited financial report of the organisation which was published on Monday via the website of the Nigerian Exchange Limited. The corporate notice signed by the Acting Company Secretary, Edward Imoedemhe, partly read, “A final dividend of N20 per share, subject to the appropriate withholding tax and approval will be paid to shareholders  whose names appear in the Register of Members as at the close of business on March 30, 2023.”